---
// No props required for now
---

<section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#181926] via-[#1a1b2e] to-background/90 overflow-hidden animate-fade-in">
  <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16 px-4">
    <!-- Illustration or SVG -->
    <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center mb-10 md:mb-0">
      <!-- Puedes reemplazar este SVG por uno propio o usar el de ejemplo -->
      <svg width="300" height="300" viewBox="0 0 300 300" fill="none">
        <g stroke="#00F0FF33" stroke-width="2">
          <rect x="20" y="40" width="100" height="100" rx="20"/>
          <rect x="180" y="40" width="100" height="100" rx="20"/>
          <rect x="100" y="160" width="100" height="100" rx="20"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="60" cy="80" r="4" fill="#00F0FF"/>
        <circle cx="110" cy="120" r="4" fill="#fff"/>
        <circle cx="200" cy="80" r="4" fill="#fff"/>
        <circle cx="250" cy="120" r="4" fill="#00F0FF"/>
        <circle cx="150" cy="200" r="4" fill="#00F0FF"/>
        <circle cx="130" cy="220" r="4" fill="#fff"/>
        <circle cx="170" cy="220" r="4" fill="#fff"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <!-- Text and Logos -->
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
      <span class="uppercase text-accent font-bold tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Integraciones</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8 text-center md:text-left leading-tight">
        Integra con más de <span class="text-accent">400+ apps</span> en segundos.
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start mb-4">
        <img src="/img/integrations/azure.png" alt="Azure" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/img/integrations/openai.png" alt="OpenAI" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/img/integrations/slack.png" alt="Slack" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/img/integrations/airtable.png" alt="Airtable" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/img/integrations/whatsapp.png" alt="WhatsApp" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/img/integrations/twilio.png" alt="Twilio" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/img/integrations/zapier.png" alt="Zapier" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/img/integrations/google.png" alt="Google" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-2 shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg max-w-xl text-center md:text-left">
        Conecta tu solución de IA con las plataformas y herramientas que ya usas. Automatiza flujos, sincroniza datos y expande el potencial de tu negocio con integraciones listas para usar.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

